{"tid":1466682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果林鄭有上連登 今晚應該笑到訓唔到","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:34.000Z","uid":184163,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dafb5a60ddb95aeb03de390b93743c05dc1a74c0","tid":1466682,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:36.000Z","msg":"811班黑警搞咁大單嘢<br />\n818民陣又吹雞<br />\n柒娥唯有今朝快閃出嚟見記者扮喊啦<br />\n點知火上加油 俾人屌到上天花板<br />\n原本佢可能仲煩緊點拆第三次百萬遊行<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n回顧返呢兩個幾月<br />\n<br />\n我哋笑班畜牲啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑班狗毫無紀律可言<br />\n笑政府班人推卸責任 互相指罵 割蓆<br />\n笑佢哋冇腦 成日衝出嚟柒<br />\n<br />\n點解班畜牲會咁乞人憎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢哋企硬唔認錯<br />\n因為佢哋周圍辣火頭<br />\n因為佢哋濫權、濫暴<br />\n<br />\n我冇資格亦冇本事講咩係啱 咩係錯<br />\n但望返今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講<br />\n我哋唔同嗰班畜牲<br />\n我哋識得思考 識得喺適當嘅時候做適當嘅嘢<br />\n我哋講好咗<br />\n要齊上齊落 要一齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e85bcc164c5bc56489e2e8b89d461c49f8c180","tid":1466682,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"自推10下<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c844105a031bbdd91cdf0995415922bede4de5d3","tid":1466682,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:53.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"1e556e82c05892edb876e20483fda56470338234","tid":1466682,"uid":184163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"02a00e9698383188a1fc055626887dbc1a40642d"